player -
Returns:
true if everthing went fine, false otherwise Updates the players longitude and latitude in the database. Updates Targetlocation, gamemode and gamestate locally. If there is a winner, then the game is finished and the winnerName is saved in the game-instance. If the player has won the game, hasWin is set to true.
